      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This car is in poor condition and definitely needs a lot of love and mechanical work to get back on the road, but it\u2019s the perfect canvas for a restorer or hobbyist. If you\u2019re looking for a vehicle with great potential that you can truly make your own, this is the one for you!",
